data.description: Come see this split entry home in Cunningham Lake! Built in 2005, this home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms (one being a primary bedroom en-suite), 2 car garage, large living space with fireplace in the basement, and walkout access from the basement. The main floor has an open concept layout between the kitchen, dining and living room with vaulted ceilings. All kitchen appliances stay, and also the washer & dryer. The primary bath has double sinks - not often found in similar properties! The backyard provides privacy being fully fenced, and has a deck and then a patio with fire pit for entertaining or relaxing. The property backs to mature trees and the neighborhood walking trail. And of course Cunningham Lake is just a few minutes down the road for all your outdoor activity desires!
